    <item>
      <title>犯罪率下降和比特币繁荣仍使萨尔瓦多追逐经济奇迹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-18/bukele-cracked-down-on-el-salvador-crime-struggles-to-boost-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利，萨尔瓦多的比特币持有量飙升。这位当选总统的移民立场可能会给他的盟友布克尔的经济计划带来更多问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-18/bukele-cracked-down-on-el-salvador-crime-struggles-to-boost-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 10:30:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
